{"tid":2061782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許智峯遭高調帶上警車 防暴拍手舉手指公叫好 喝斥記者「曱甴議員都唔影，你影我做乜。」","createTime":"2020-06-12T15:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T16:57:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4133f2ef46893f2796c8319e07f11bf2a92bcb85","tid":2061782,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074471&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=592750e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074471&h=8b51f457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074471</a><br />\n<br />\n許智峯晚上在銅鑼灣記利佐治街被捕，他晚上在崇光百貨對出，即金百利商場外執行職務時，遭警方強行拉入封鎖線範圍。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯及後遭防暴警察拖行至金百利商場較近商舖的範圍，最後被警察高調押上警車。許智峯在被鎖上索帶時遭屈曲手腕。有在場的防暴警察拍手和對同事舉起手指公，記者欲拍攝時遭到對方喝斥，稱「曱甴議員都唔影，你影我做乜。」"},{"pid":"02e930a1fe7ae4aa2166095498340e41813402e7","tid":2061782,"uid":289978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"因為要影曱甴黑警"},{"pid":"7c9a9792a62eedfdb101292bb31120e79d684983","tid":2061782,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇片放上Twitter"},{"pid":"e8effcfe6b18db0b8c7ede0c2f6ca595ccd2b7da","tid":2061782,"uid":256336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0971ab2dfd79f3ce7d31f1b91594f3d3d8c4575e","tid":2061782,"uid":90601,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"乜撚野都係曱甴<br />\n全世界得佢地係人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92d9efa018f43e475140f7be3e658c1b0d47d04","tid":2061782,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite